OL,3,CWatkins' accused killer only felt
OL,4,Cguilt for paedophile's victims, court
OL,5,Chears
OL,7,FAn inmate accused of murdering former
OL,8,FLostprophets singer Ian Watkins
OL,9,Fclaimed he only felt guilt for the
OL,10,Fpaedophile's victims.
OL,12,FRico Gedel is on trial alongside
OL,13,FSamuel Dodsworth for murdering Watkins
OL,14,Fat HMP Wakefield last year.
OL,16,FThe former frontman was serving a 29-
OL,17,Fyear sentence for child sex offences
OL,18,Fat the high security jail when he was
OL,19,Ffatally stabbed on October 11.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/8
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,364,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F363A1778782268
OL,3,CWatkins' accused killer only felt
OL,4,Cguilt for paedophile's victims, court
OL,5,Chears
OL,7,FGedel, 25, has previously admitted to
OL,8,Fstabbing Watkins, claiming he had
OL,9,Fpreviously requested to be moved from
OL,10,Fsharing a wing with sex offenders and
OL,11,Fthat he had only intended to injure
OL,12,Fhim.
OL,14,FTaking the stand at Leeds Crown Court
OL,15,Fon Thursday, Gedel was asked by
OL,16,FRichard Wright KC whether he was
OL,17,F"pleased" Watkins had died, to which
OL,18,Fhe replied "somewhat".
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/8
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,364,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F363A1778782268
OL,3,CWatkins' accused killer only felt
OL,4,Cguilt for paedophile's victims, court
OL,5,Chears
OL,7,FMr Wright, defending Dodsworth,
OL,8,Fsuggested, "you're certainly not
OL,9,Flosing sleep over it?" Gedel replied:
OL,10,F"No, not really."
OL,12,F"What I wanted to say is, the only
OL,13,Fguilt I would feel about this is how
OL,14,Fhis victims felt," he continued.
OL,16,F"I know from my own experiences, with
OL,17,Ffriends and family being sexually
OL,18,Fassaulted, I don't know if they would
OL,19,Fhave wanted that (Watkins's death).
OL,20,FBut that's my only guilt."
OL,26,@tD@AOUxD@AOU|D@ZO]
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/8
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,364,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F363A1778782268
OL,3,CWatkins' accused killer only felt
OL,4,Cguilt for paedophile's victims, court
OL,5,Chears
OL,7,FBeing asked to clarify whether he
OL,8,Fmeant Watkins' victims may have wanted
OL,9,Fhim to spend his full sentence, Gedel
OL,10,Fsaid: "I felt a bit guilty for them
OL,11,Fbecause they didn't get that
OL,12,Fopportunity."
OL,14,FThe trial heard Gedel was already
OL,15,Fserving a 27-year minimum life
OL,16,Fsentence after being convicted of
OL,17,Fmurder in his early 20s, a crime which
OL,18,Fhe still denied.
OL,26,@rD@GOUtD@MO]
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G4/8
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,364,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F363A1778782268
OL,3,CWatkins' accused killer only felt
OL,4,Cguilt for paedophile's victims, court
OL,5,Chears
OL,7,FMr Wright pointed out Gedel had
OL,8,Fpreviously changed his account three
OL,9,Ftimes, most recently the day before
OL,10,Ftaking the stand, and was now claiming
OL,11,Fhis co-accused Dodsworth had handed
OL,12,Fhim the knife.
OL,14,FDodsworth's defence barrister
OL,15,Fsuggested Gedel was now saying this
OL,16,Fbecause it was "convenient" and
OL,17,F"frankly, it's good fun".
OL,19,F"I did get the knife from Dodsworth,"
OL,20,FGedel replied.
OL,26,@{D@AOU{D@eO]
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G5/8
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,364,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F363A1778782268
OL,3,CWatkins' accused killer only felt
OL,4,Cguilt for paedophile's victims, court
OL,5,Chears
OL,7,FHe then told prosecutor Tom Storey KC:
OL,8,F"I don't like fighting, in every fight
OL,9,Fthere is a possibility I could lose
OL,10,Fand I don't want to end up injured.
OL,12,F"There are serial killers in
OL,13,FWakefield. I am around serious people
OL,14,Flike that, I know the possibility for
OL,15,Fme could also be death."
OL,17,FBody-worn footage played in court
OL,18,Fshowed Gedel being held by prison
OL,19,Fguards minutes after the attack while
OL,20,Fefforts were made to help Watkins.
OL,26,@pD@AOUtD@AOUwD@XO]
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G6/8
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,364,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36307
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F363A1778782268
OL,3,CWatkins' accused killer only felt
OL,4,Cguilt for paedophile's victims, court
OL,5,Chears
OL,7,FIn it, Gedel could be seen smiling and
OL,8,Fsaying: "Hopefully he goes to sleep."
OL,10,FGedel told the court: "There was part
OL,11,Fof me that wanted him to die, there
OL,12,Fwas another part of me that didn't
OL,13,Fwant him to die. That was a bad
OL,14,Fconcoction."
OL,16,FHis explanation for grinning meanwhile
OL,17,Fwas that it "was the only way of
OL,18,Fmasking my emotions in front of other
OL,19,Fpeople".
OL,26,@rD@WOUvD@LO]
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G7/8
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
