OL,3,CWatkins' accused killer only felt
OL,4,Cguilt for paedophile's victims, court
OL,5,Chears
OL,7,FGedel and Dodsworth, a convicted
OL,8,Frapist, both deny Watkins' murder and
OL,9,Fpossession of a makeshift knife. The
OL,10,Ftrial continues.
OL,12,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,13,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,14,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,15,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,16,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,17,Fbelow...
